# Fix panels in control center

```
cd /usr/share/applications
sudo sed -i 's/\(OnlyShowIn.*GNOME.*\)/\1Awesome;/' *.desktop
#sudo sed -i 's/\(OnlyShowIn.*GNOME.*\)/\1Awesome;/' *panel.desktop

cd /etc/xdg/autostart
sudo sed -i 's/\(OnlyShowIn.*Unity.*\)/\1Awesome;/' *.desktop
sudo sed -i 's/Awesome;Awesome/Awesome/' *.desktop
```
